  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/b0d302c117c9dbdef81f48a40d17c37d.avif?t=1734960755\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras_big/b0d302c117c9dbdef81f48a40d17c37d.avif?t=1734960755 width=800 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FallNation: Lost Stories is a procedurally generated first-person roguelike filled with handcrafted locations, powerful upgrades, and an evolving storyline. Discover deeper questions about the fate of humanity in the cosmos, dive into the adventure and discover what lies beyond! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/74f1b0b6a89d0231cf7792265765afe7.poster.avif?t=1734960755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/74f1b0b6a89d0231cf7792265765afe7.webm?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/74f1b0b6a89d0231cf7792265765afe7.mp4?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/9cb8212aebcbd925908af6cc717b7f6e.avif?t=1734960755\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras_big/9cb8212aebcbd925908af6cc717b7f6e.avif?t=1734960755 width=800 height=59 /></span><strong>Time is of the essence</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each game, or run, will conclude when your character's objective has been fulfilled, or when you succumb to death. Death, however, comes swiftly: a toxic gas fills each level, and your oxygen mask has limited time. You won't be able to stop as you advance to the next level. Whether collecting keys or eliminating a certain number of enemies, your time will be limited, and your judgment essential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/e2d3fcd3aa058012ccffd3348bc4137f.poster.avif?t=1734960755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/e2d3fcd3aa058012ccffd3348bc4137f.webm?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/e2d3fcd3aa058012ccffd3348bc4137f.mp4?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Every bullet counts</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each shot can mean the difference between life and death. With challenging combat and limited resources, you'll need to plan every move and choose your strategy wisely as you face the horrors of the bunker. Master the art of precision and management to survive in a world where each attempt brings you one step closer to the truth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/b07679a5a6d4b7cf4193e09f489b44d5.poster.avif?t=1734960755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/b07679a5a6d4b7cf4193e09f489b44d5.webm?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/b07679a5a6d4b7cf4193e09f489b44d5.mp4?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/47c5f97e8461798af1a5a228a799530d.avif?t=1734960755\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras_big/47c5f97e8461798af1a5a228a799530d.avif?t=1734960755 width=800 height=59 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five years after a mysterious event that changed the world, the sun dims and the cold advances. Black cracks appear where there was once life, and strange beings walk among us. In FallNation: Lost Stories, you'll delve into the epicenter of this enigma, where the normal and the paranormal cross paths. Discover the secrets that could be the key to saving humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Contributions</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the collaboration of the \"Comunidad de Madrid\" (Spain) throught the support program: \"Creación y desarrollo de proyectos de videojuegos.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/b65082608c7c8763052014a00a3149e2.avif?t=1734960755\" width=128 height=166 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/b0d302c117c9dbdef81f48a40d17c37d.avif?t=1734960755\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras_big/b0d302c117c9dbdef81f48a40d17c37d.avif?t=1734960755 width=800 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FallNation: Lost Stories is a procedurally generated first-person roguelike filled with handcrafted locations, powerful upgrades, and an evolving storyline. Discover deeper questions about the fate of humanity in the cosmos, dive into the adventure and discover what lies beyond! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/74f1b0b6a89d0231cf7792265765afe7.poster.avif?t=1734960755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/74f1b0b6a89d0231cf7792265765afe7.webm?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/74f1b0b6a89d0231cf7792265765afe7.mp4?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/9cb8212aebcbd925908af6cc717b7f6e.avif?t=1734960755\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras_big/9cb8212aebcbd925908af6cc717b7f6e.avif?t=1734960755 width=800 height=59 /></span><strong>Time is of the essence</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each game, or run, will conclude when your character's objective has been fulfilled, or when you succumb to death. Death, however, comes swiftly: a toxic gas fills each level, and your oxygen mask has limited time. You won't be able to stop as you advance to the next level. Whether collecting keys or eliminating a certain number of enemies, your time will be limited, and your judgment essential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/e2d3fcd3aa058012ccffd3348bc4137f.poster.avif?t=1734960755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/e2d3fcd3aa058012ccffd3348bc4137f.webm?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/e2d3fcd3aa058012ccffd3348bc4137f.mp4?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Every bullet counts</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each shot can mean the difference between life and death. With challenging combat and limited resources, you'll need to plan every move and choose your strategy wisely as you face the horrors of the bunker. Master the art of precision and management to survive in a world where each attempt brings you one step closer to the truth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/b07679a5a6d4b7cf4193e09f489b44d5.poster.avif?t=1734960755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/b07679a5a6d4b7cf4193e09f489b44d5.webm?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/b07679a5a6d4b7cf4193e09f489b44d5.mp4?t=1734960755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/47c5f97e8461798af1a5a228a799530d.avif?t=1734960755\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras_big/47c5f97e8461798af1a5a228a799530d.avif?t=1734960755 width=800 height=59 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five years after a mysterious event that changed the world, the sun dims and the cold advances. Black cracks appear where there was once life, and strange beings walk among us. In FallNation: Lost Stories, you'll delve into the epicenter of this enigma, where the normal and the paranormal cross paths. Discover the secrets that could be the key to saving humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Contributions</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the collaboration of the \"Comunidad de Madrid\" (Spain) throught the support program: \"Creación y desarrollo de proyectos de videojuegos.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774800/extras/b65082608c7c8763052014a00a3149e2.avif?t=1734960755\" width=128 height=166 /></span></p>",
